These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, onion, lettuce
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, doctor, writer
1. the person eating cucumber is the doctor##1
2. the writer is on the right of the doctor##1
3. the writer is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
4. the doctor is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Food   | cucumber | lettuce | onion    |
| Job     | doctor    | writer       | pilot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
City: venice, boston, edinburgh
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, puzzles, baking
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person traveling to boston is the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| City     | edinburgh | venice | boston  |
| Hobby   | drawing  | puzzles  | baking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
3 different pets are kept: horse, turtle, dog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, skateboarding, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far left or far right##3
2. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the turtle is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Pet           | dog | turtle | horse |
| Sport   | rowing        | ice-hockey    | skateboarding        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, water, lemonade
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, prince, vegafina
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the bongani-smoker is between the person drinking lemonade and the vegafina-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | lemonade | water | almond-milk |
| Cigar     | prince  | bongani    | vegafina  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, teacher, project-manager
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, mirinda, fanta
1. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the musician##3
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the musician##1
4. the musician is between the teacher and the person drinking fanta##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Job   | teacher | musician | project-manager |
| Beverage     | mirinda   | iced-tea   | fanta   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig, frog
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, techno, funk
1. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of trance##1
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3
4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Pet   | frog | snake | guinea-pig      |
| Music-Genre     | techno  | funk | trance |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, 7up
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, sunflower, amaryllis
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea  | 7up    | cola       |
| Flower   | sunflower | amaryllis | poppy |

