.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, chess, go
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, martial-arts, zombie
1. the person playing backgammon is the person watching action movies##1
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
3. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Game   | go        | chess  | backgammon   |
| Movie-Genre       | zombie | martial-arts | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-9::.
3 different pets are kept: lizard, rat, goldfish
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, sunflower, daisy
1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| Pet           | lizard | rat | goldfish |
| Flower   | daisy    | azalea | sunflower     |

