.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, cricket-polo, cricket
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, skydiving, rock-climbing
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |
| Sport      | surfing | cricket-polo    | cricket      |
| Hobby   | skydiving       | drawing | rock-climbing |

