.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-11::.
3 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, cat
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, prince, dunhill
1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the right of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the prince-smoker is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2       |       3        |
| Pet   | cat | bird         | hamster          |
| Cigar        | tiparillo | prince | dunhill |

