.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  bartender, pilot, musician
City: edinburgh, miami, venice
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the bartender and the pilot##2
2. the person traveling to miami is the pilot##1
3. the pilot is on the left of the musician##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the bartender##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Job      | pilot    | musician    | bartender  |
| City   | miami | edinburgh | venice |

