.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, country, ambient
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, pink, black
1. the person who likes purple is on the far left or far right##3
2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
3. the person who likes black is between the person who likes pink and the person who likes purple##2
4. the person who likes purple is the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | ambient | country |
| Color           | pink    | black    | purple       |

