.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, february, january
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, amaryllis, azalea
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who growsazalea##3
3. the person who growsazalea is the person who growsazalea##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Birthday   | january    | august   | february |
| Flower   | amaryllis | azalea | zinnia |

