.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, hot-chocolate
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, bus, roller
1. the person driving the bus is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person driving the roller and the person driving the taxi##2
3. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person drinking milk##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | tea | hot-chocolate | milk |
| Transport   | taxi     | bus  | roller    |

