.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-17::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, r&b, techno
The people have 3 different jobs:  security-guard, musician, chef
1. the security-guard is the fan of electronic##1
2. the security-guard is on the far right##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
4. the fan of r&b is the chef##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |    3    |
| Music-Genre       | techno    | r&b | electronic  |
| Job   | musician | chef        | security-guard |

