.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-18::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, security-guard, manager
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, polish, indian
1. the security-guard is in the middle##1
2. the security-guard is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the manager is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
4. the russian is on the left of the security-guard##1
5. the security-guard is the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |       3       |
| Job       | photographer | security-guard | manager |
| Nationality   | russian  | polish   | indian    |

