.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-19::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, pony, fish
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, climbing, golf
1. the owner of the ferret is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |
| Pet          | pony | fish    | ferret |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing | lacrosse  |

