.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, sunflower, daffodil
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, chinchilla, lizard
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
2. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Flower      | daffodil    | sunflower | orchid         |
| Pet   | lizard | chinchilla  | rabbit |

 